---
// AboutTeaser.astro — sub-page summary on home page.
// Full bio lives at /about.
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-num">§ 03 — About</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Built like a senior IC. <em>Runs like a consultant.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-teaser">
      <div class="about-quote">
        I take a small number of engagements at a time. The focus is shipping
        AI on the Microsoft stack — particularly when the environment is
        regulated, complex, or built on .NET.
      </div>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>
          I'm a senior platform engineer and Microsoft Certified Azure Solutions
          Architect Expert based in Florida. I've spent the last several years as
          the platform engineer on a multi-tenant fintech platform running real
          PCI-regulated workloads at production scale.
        </p>
        <p>
          Early Bird Solutions is the consulting practice I run alongside that
          work. If you're considering working together, the easiest path is a
          short call.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="about-link">
          More about my background <span>→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-teaser {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 100px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-quote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-quote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 64px;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 0;
    position: relative;
    top: 14px;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .about-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .about-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-teaser {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
